title: Volleyball Roundup: Bulldogs top Aces at home
text:
Volleyball Roundup: Bulldogs top Aces at home 11:13 p.m. EDT October 8, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Bloom Carroll 3, Amanda Clearcreek 2 
The Bulldogs won a tough match at home against the Aces in Mid State League-Buckeye Divsion play 23-25, 22-25, 25-23, 25-23 and 15-8. 
Bloom Carroll was led by Madelyn Nye with 15 kills, Emily Simon had 13 kills, Alayna Ireland had 10 kills and Madison Compton had 7 kills. 
Fairfield Union 3, Liberty Union 0 
The Falcons won an away match Tuesday over host Liberty Union 25-22, 25-14 and 25-23. Katie Gordon led Fairfield Union with 5 kills and 2 blocks. Read or Share this story: http://ohne.ws/1Ll3dTr More Stories
